{"tid":1128624,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"偉大！C.朗拿度解鎖球會生涯600球 比美斯快一步","createTime":"2019-04-28T02:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T08:48:20.000Z","uid":173952,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"08e08c912b8853147e8a46aeef054851c1056dce","tid":1128624,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T02:55:56.000Z","msg":"C.朗拿度解鎖球會600球<br />\n<br />\n  在祖雲達斯與國米的比賽中，C.朗拿度攻入了扳平比數的一球，而這粒入球也是他職業生涯為球會球隊攻入的第600球。<br />\n<br />\n  意甲第34輪，國米主場迎戰祖記。上半場尼恩高蘭為國米打破僵局，而在下半場第62分鐘，C.朗拿度接比真歷的傳球，左腳低射破門，把比數改寫為1-1。<br />\n<br />\n  對於C.朗拿度來說，這粒入球的有著非凡的意義。這是他球會生涯的第600粒入球，包括為葡萄牙體育攻入的5球，為曼聯攻入的118球，為皇馬攻入的450球和為祖記攻入的27球。<br />\n<br />\nC.朗拿度600球<br />\n<br />\n  如果按賽事劃分，那麼C.朗拿度的600球中有311粒西甲入球，126粒歐冠盃入球，84粒英超入球，22粒西班牙盃入球，20粒意甲入球，13粒足總盃入球，7粒世冠盃入球，4粒聯賽盃入球，4粒西班牙超級盃入球，3粒葡超入球，2粒葡萄牙杯入球，2粒歐洲超級盃入球，1粒歐冠盃資格賽入球和1粒意大利超級盃入球。<br />\n<br />\n  美斯與C.朗拿度的球會入球數差距只有2粒，在今晚之後，美斯的球會生涯入球數來到了598粒，而C.朗拿度先一步解鎖了600球的成就。"},{"pid":"db05948f5ed99fcb9f7d90385192ad763fca03af","tid":1128624,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T03:24:27.000Z","msg":"球入波靚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b0d4a81c78855559c601007cf5bff7e02ee516","tid":1128624,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T03:24:49.000Z","msg":"唔過半頁"},{"pid":"4db655b66b3fa4a2831a091f566c0f4ce73f40fc","tid":1128624,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:17:36.000Z","msg":"入球機器？C.朗拿度連續10年聯賽入球超20個<br />\n<br />\n朗迷呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85bc806cb3a775939f9764e7824f8744eea3e84","tid":1128624,"uid":34571,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:19:37.000Z","msg":"踢多兩季多兩球"},{"pid":"2d0ca723edf0de049f79eae375f962605f41cfcf","tid":1128624,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:20:33.000Z","msg":"2014/15賽季，他為皇馬在西甲攻入48球，創近10年聯賽入球最高紀錄"},{"pid":"97f8ed1b4a7d938e53f3cd5e22a8bfba1666d335","tid":1128624,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:26:54.000Z","msg":"左腳貼柱入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4211d1cfc176ecae26e21d35c588546a28801479","tid":1128624,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:28:13.000Z","msg":"快樂足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcdaf77e8b85b62829c5af5196dcf59f6754da1b","tid":1128624,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T06:33:26.000Z","msg":"去中國聯賽入多600 粒啦"},{"pid":"49ef58b124aba6cb3db5500bdf05def099e90246","tid":1128624,"uid":35877,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"大兩年喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多得2球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2cbf4b09cdb35aa5ab28533feb34f00b9980f3","tid":1128624,"uid":200139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T07:05:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fdcb364dc58677f4445f22ff4a058d983b01838e","tid":1128624,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"49ef58b124aba6cb3db5500bdf05def099e90246","tid":1128624,"uid":35877,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"大兩年喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多得2球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T07:14:57.000Z","msg":"C朗起碼踢到45歲，美斯35左右收皮"},{"pid":"4b77e223046cc569823906207f7cc883c6ab258c","tid":1128624,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdcb364dc58677f4445f22ff4a058d983b01838e","tid":1128624,"uid":173952,"like":0,